{"tid":1575989,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"識「剪片」既同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:27:13.000Z","uid":322608,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c54c3981b2aff49b9fedd38a32fac948350cc5c2","tid":1575989,"uid":322608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"識「剪片」既同我入黎！<br />\n<br />\n大家睇完 Netflix 都眼濕濕，好想自己整一部...<br />\n<br />\n《Winter of Fire》係2015年9月Netflix上架，但烏克蘭示威運動是2014年2月23日完結！<br />\n<br />\n如果《WoF》能夠2013年12月聖誕檔期上架，會唔會死少啲人，早啲取得成功？<br />\n<br />\n我唔知答案，但我覺得要試行呢條路：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港反送中紀錄片（共三集），趕及2019年11月於Netflix上架</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n集合所有本地記者／攝錄者的影片，剪輯香港版本的《WoF》<br />\n《Be Water》<br />\n共三集<br />\n第一集：勇氣<br />\n第二集：看不見的希望<br />\n第三集：(待續) 榮光歸於香港 <br />\n<br />\n要有：音樂、煽情、年青人的面對生與死、參與者的初心、世界價值觀、政府所有黑暗行的的報署及目的等等<br />\n<br />\n半島電視台已經做左一個好例子，但耐何佢地只能以新聞透視既各度去報道，而且上唔到Netflix，全球訂閱用戶人數1.48億既平台。<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong's Summer of Defiance - Part 1 | People and Power<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WDpPQ63WgFM&amp;t=35s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWDpPQ63WgFM%26t%3D35s&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=0d56ea30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WDpPQ63WgFM&amp;t=35s</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong's Summer of Defiance - Part 2 | People and Power<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_mZLitD7x8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl_mZLitD7x8&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=223c6444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l_mZLitD7x8</a><br />\n<br />\n如何將影片於Netflix上架<br />\nHow To Submit Your Project To Netflix<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.filmmakingstuff.com/sell-a-movie-to-netflix/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmmakingstuff.com%2Fsell-a-movie-to-netflix%2F&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=eb2b4711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.filmmakingstuff.com/sell-a-movie-to-netflix/</a><br />\n<br />\n目標：<br />\n影片觸及率要非常高<br />\n提名2020奧斯卡/金球獎"},{"pid":"1ff4f22f53dc01941c6f5707d8f39674fc9715c2","tid":1575989,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00650d1a553084ecd14287c047b22816ee5c6bab","tid":1575989,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77e09e03f065fc978268ee3da5dfbd6c0fb78c0f","tid":1575989,"uid":208253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b8937ce6a5202fa07330151ccf91477c6a98eac","tid":1575989,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望netflix唔奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b05d3ee5c8439bb49edfe1f0a50b5de631e4595","tid":1575989,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"以前已經諗過 終於有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c24f1312b0632e68617359a38ad875ec3d9c2f9","tid":1575989,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f89ee7fcf34680d88fe8345aab577f45941ff7fd","tid":1575989,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHTzyJS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F